'''QF1磅炮'''是一款由英國研發生產的37毫米[[機炮|機炮]]。因其發射時會發出砰砰的聲音，QF1磅炮得到了「砰砰炮」的諢名。QF1磅砰砰炮是世界上第一款機炮，曾被多個國家當作步兵支援武器和輕型[[防空炮|防空炮]]使用<ref>{{cite book|title=The Waverley pictorial dictionary (Volume SIX)|publisher=Waverley Book Co|location=London|pages=3335|url=https://archive.org/stream/waverleypictoria06wheeuoft#page/3334/mode/1up}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bwm.org.au/site/Weapons.asp|title=Weapons|publisher=Australian Boer War Memorial Committee|accessdate=2008-08-28|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080719132235/http://www.bwm.org.au/site/Weapons.asp|archivedate=2008-07-19}}</ref><ref>"...my paper strength will be 2,400 mounted men, 6 guns, and 8 pom-poms". Brigadier [[Henry_Rawlinson,_1st_Baron_Rawlinson|Henry Rawlinson]], 2 January 1902, in South Africa. From "The Life of General Lord Rawlinson of Trent", by Sir Frederick Maurice. London: Cassell, 1928</ref>。

